oracle.apps.saf.ta.jaudit.core.annotations
Annotation Type AuditElement

@Target(value=METHOD)
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface AuditElement

Indicates analyzer visitor methods to enter for given Xml Element names. This annotation should be used to annotate analyzer visitor methods that audit only particular Xml Element names and Namespace. This annotation is only valid for classes extending AbstractXmlAnalyzer.

For example:

@AuditElement(names = "set", namespace = "http://java.sun.com/jsp/jstl/core")
public void enterSet(AuditContext context, ElementFacade elementFacade)

See Also:
AbstractXmlAnalyzer
